      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of August 8 Company News column on job cuts at Fruit of the Loom factories</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A brief report by The Associated Press in the Company News column of Business Day yesterday about job cuts at Fruit of the Loom factories overstated the extent of the cuts. The company plans to eliminate 4,800 jobs at six plants, not 5,100 at seven plants.</p>
      </block>
